# React 18 + Vite 7 Template

Out-of-the-box stack for SPAs with modern DX and zero vendor lock-in.

## Stack

‚Ä¢ **React 18** + **TypeScript** (strict)  
‚Ä¢ **Vite 7** ‚Äì lightning-fast dev server & build  
‚Ä¢ **Tailwind 4** + shadcn/ui components  
‚Ä¢ **TanStack Query v5** ‚Äì data-fetching, caching, retries  
‚Ä¢ **React Router 7** ‚Äì client-side routing  
‚Ä¢ **Axios** ‚Äì single HTTP wrapper with auth, timing, error mapping  
‚Ä¢ **Zod** ‚Äì runtime schema validation & typed responses  
‚Ä¢ **Vitest + RTL + MSW** ‚Äì unit/integration test harness  
‚Ä¢ **GitHub Actions** CI (lint ‚Üí test ‚Üí build)  
‚Ä¢ **Dependabot** weekly dependency updates

## Getting Started

```bash
pnpm i        # or npm install / yarn
pnpm dev      # start Vite dev server  http://localhost:5173

pnpm test     # run vitest in watch mode
pnpm build    # type-check & build production assets to /dist
pnpm preview  # serve /dist locally to verify
```

## Project Layout

```
src/
  lib/              # shared singletons (http, queryClient)
  schemas/          # Zod schemas & types
  services/         # API calls (axios + schema parsing)
  hooks/            # reusable data hooks (useUsers)
  pages/            # route components (Home, UsersPage)
  components/       # UI (shadcn ui/, ErrorBoundary)
```

## Extending

‚Ä¢ **Add an API resource**

1. Define schema in `src/schemas/`.
2. Create service in `src/services/` that parses response.
3. Expose a hook in `src/hooks/` using TanStack Query.
4. Consume from a page/component.

‚Ä¢ **Add a route**: create a page component and register it in `src/App.tsx` `<Routes>` list.

‚Ä¢ **Run CI locally**: `node .github/workflows/ci.yml` steps (lint, test, build) ‚Äì matches GitHub Actions.

## Dependency Updates

Dependabot is configured (`.github/dependabot.yml`) to open weekly PRs for npm packages except React 19 until ecosystem support lands.

